parameter.description:
Tech stack dictionary from identify_tech_stack().
Expected format: { "web_servers": [{"name": "Apache", "version": "2.4.49", "confidence": "high"}], "languages": [{"name": "PHP", "version": "7.4.3"}], "frameworks": [{"name": "Laravel", "version": "8.0"}], "cms": [{"name": "WordPress", "version": "5.8.2"}], "databases": [{"name": "MySQL", "version": "8.0.26"}] }
The function extracts all technologies WITH versions and queries CVE databases.

returns.description:
{
  "status": "success",
  "hypothesis_id": "H-0042",
  "cve_id": "CVE-2021-41773",
  "enriched_data": {
    "description": "Path traversal in Apache HTTP Server 2.4.49...",
    "cvss_score": 7.5,
    "severity": "HIGH",
    "references": [...]
  },
